list.comment: Mapped Explorer's Pack content items on resources, created addItemPack on CharacterClassBusiness for Explorer's Pack and created getMiscItem on JsonMapper

task.summary: Default task
Included Spring Boot dependencies
Updated pom.xml with Spring Boot dependencies
Corrected Spring Boot dependency on POM and created a mock controller
Service generating character created and a new "Human" race created
Basic mocking services created
JsonMapper class created and tested with a CharacterRace generation
CharacterRaceController testes with Mocked DAO created
Refactored the CharacterRaceController to use Path Parameters instead of Query String Parameters
CharacterRaceDao now using HashMaps to be able to fetch objects by its id
JsonMapper getAllRaces() function refactored to get all files in the json.races folder instead of having to add files one by one.
CharacterSavingThrows class refactored to get only boolean values instead of ValueAdvantage
Barbarian and Bard classes jsons created
All classes added as jsons
CharacterRaceDao refactored to get all races from json files on the resource folder.
Randomizers taken out of CharacterBusiness and a new Randomizer class created with a getRandomRace() method. Unit test for that method created
Added resistances to the Character Class
Created an endpoint to get a random number based on a dice roll
Created Unit Tests for the Randomizer class and fixed class jsons
Created Unit Tests for 100% of the methods on CharacterBusiness
Fixed a bug on the getRandomRace and getRandomClass methods that were sometimes returning null objects
The generateRandomCharacter method on CharacterBusiness class now calls applyCharacterClass on a random CharacterClass.
Created the methods to generate random height based on Race
Finished creating the background jsons.
Created the CharacterBackground class.
Created the methods to get a CharacterBackground from the json files in the resource folder inside the JsonMapper class, with unit tests.
Created a method to get a random Background from the json files in the Resource folder
Created a method to apply all CharacterSkills from the Background to a single character
Refactored addCharacterSkillAdvantages to not overwrite already set Skill Advantages on a character
Created CharacterCurrencyBusiness with AddMoney and SubtractMoney methods
Created getRandomListItemString on Randomizer
Created applyBackground on CharacterBusiness
Created getRandomAlignment in Randomizer
Created calculateNewCharacter in CharacterBusiness and added a new constructor to Dice to use "XdY" notation.
Created calculateSkillValues in CharacterBusiness
Deleted unused CharacterSkillsBusiness class
Created a method to generate a random Character in CharacterController and fixed several business bugs
Created a calculateProficiencyBonus on CharacterBusiness
Created generateBalancedAbilityScores in Randomizer to improve random AbilityScore generation
Mapped armor and weapons jsons
Removed Starting Equipment from CharacterClass and corresponding jsons to implement on CharacterClassBusiness
Created methods to get an specific Weapon/Armor or all Weapons/Armors in JsonMapper
Created methods to get a random armor and get a random weapon
Corrected the HP calculation to get the HitDice sides and add the Constitution modifier
Made it so when creating a random character, the currentHp will always be the MaxHP
Corrected the number of total Hit Dice when generating a random Character
Randomized the height and weight based on races when generating a random character
Created getAllWeaponsByCategory on Randomizer and created CharacterClassBusiness with getStartingEquipmentOptions for Barbarian
